powerpc/watchpoint: Rename current DAWR macros

Power10 is introducing second DAWR. Use real register names from ISA
for current macros:
  s/SPRN_DAWR/SPRN_DAWR0/
  s/SPRN_DAWRX/SPRN_DAWRX0/

